# What Happened?

We discovered:

✅ Kafka works

✅ Producer works

✅ Consumer works

✅ Spark works

❌ Spark + Kafka Connector fails on Windows because Spark 4.x is trying to invoke Hadoop utilities (`winutils.exe`). 

This is actually a known Windows issue.

---

